### 6.2 Capabilities
- **250 concurrent vehicles** via `asyncio` (20 manually defined + 230 auto-generated)
- Configurable vehicle profiles (sedan, truck, sport) with different temp/SOC/speed ranges
- 5 fault-injection scenarios:
  - **Normal Drive**: Natural speed/SOC fluctuations
  - **Battery Drain**: Accelerated battery depletion
  - **Temperature Spike**: Overheating simulation
  - **Network Dropout**: Intermittent connectivity loss
  - **OTA Trigger**: Periodic OTA update requests
- YAML-based fleet configuration
- Auto-generation of vehicle fleets with configurable prefixes

