## 8. Known Limitations (To Solve in Major Project)

| Limitation | Impact |
|------------|--------|
| No persistent database | All data lost when Redis TTL (120s) expires |
| No authentication | All endpoints are open, no user roles |
| No historical data | Only last-known-state snapshots available |
| No ML/AI | Purely reactive system, no predictions |
| Polling-only frontend | 3–5s polling intervals, not truly real-time |
| No observability | No Prometheus, Grafana, or structured logging |

