# Part II — Major Project Plan (7th Semester 🚀)

## 9. Vision

Transform Axion from a functional prototype into an **intelligent, stateful, enterprise-ready fleet management platform** with persistent storage, authentication, real-time communication, ML-powered predictive analytics, and full observability.

## 10. Target Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    SIM["Python Simulator"] -->|REST/MQTT| GW["Spring Boot API Gateway"]
    
    GW --> KT["Kafka: telemetry.normal"]
    GW --> KO["Kafka: ota.events"]
    
    KT --> TC["TwinConsumer"]
    KO --> OC["OTA Consumer"]
    
    TC --> REDIS["Redis<br/>Live State"]
    TC --> TSDB["TimescaleDB<br/>Time-Series"]
    TC --> PG["PostgreSQL<br/>Campaigns, Users, Audit"]
    
    OC --> PG
    
    TSDB --> ML["FastAPI ML Service"]
    ML -->|Predictions| GW
    
    GW -->|WebSocket STOMP| FRONT["React Dashboard<br/>JWT Auth + RBAC"]
    
    GW --> PROM["Prometheus"]
    PROM --> GRAF["Grafana Dashboards"]
```

